    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0390回】　按正確順序修行應做之事</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0301-0400/t-0390-aiki-proper-order/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
